backend directory must have a Google Vision API credentials JSON, the file name must be "vision-api.json"

JSON Structure:

{
  "type": ,
  "project_id": ,
  "private_key_id": ,
  "private_key": ,
  "client_email": ,
  "client_id": ,
  "auth_uri": ,
  "token_uri": ,
  "auth_provider_x509_cert_url": ,
  "client_x509_cert_url": ,
  "universe_domain":
}